snippet.title: Five Nights at Candy's 3 Trailer
snippet.description:
=== READ THE DESCRIPTION PLEASE ===
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Please do not re-upload this video on YouTube or anywhere else, you can do a reaction video or
show the video in your own video, but you can't just re-upload the video with no changes made.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
I know I have been tough with my rules around copyright.

But IT'S OK TO PLAY THE GAME ON YOUR YOUTUBE CHANNEL, even if you don't credit me!
Of course you still can't tell people that you or somebody else owns/made the game.

And I guess it would be the best for your fans if you put a download link to the game
in the game-video's description. But you don't HAVE to...
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Trailer Music: "They Come In The Night" --- http://www.newgrounds.com/audio/listen/547936
By: Usernamemyarse --- http://usernamemyarse.newgrounds.com/
The trailer music has been shortened from the original, and the volume has been balanced.

The official game page --- http://gamejolt.com/games/five-nights-at-candy-s-3-official/130420

My official Tumblr --- http://the-interdimensional-seeker.tumblr.com/
My official Twitter --- https://twitter.com/Emilmacko
My official Reddit --- http://www.reddit.com/user/Emilmacko/
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
